 om/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/5ba5e15c-3943-47a0-b455-8ba5d56e3ca2.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://badastronautbeer.com/wp-content/uploads/2
 025/08/5ba5e15c-3943-47a0-b455-8ba5d56e3ca2.jpg
UID:ssjne5lPcmJGR8XTiNovN
SUMMARY:Williams Writers Workshop: Comedy Writers Room
DTSTAMP:20260618T044225Z
DTSTART:20260701T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Bad Astronaut Presents \nWILLIAMS WRITER WORKSHOP with WILLIAM 
	LODEN JR.\nEvery Wednesday | 6 – 8 PM | Free Entry \nJoin local comics in 
