IMAGE;VALUE=URI;DISPLAY=BADGE;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.eurekaheights.
 com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/general-trivia.jpg
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://www.eurekaheights.com/wp-content/uploads/
 2025/06/general-trivia.jpg
UID:Tb1YqI37Ot0XiDzVhOPns
SUMMARY:Trivia Night
DTSTAMP:20260618T044225Z
DTSTART:20260729T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:It’s the battle of the brains! Join us every Wednesday at 7 PM 
	as we test how much random knowledge you’ve retained since high school.\nW
